<section id="header1" class="container my-3 w-75"> 
    <h1 class="font-italic text-center display-1 mb-3">12 Pins</h1>
    <p class="text-center h5 mb-5">We have the ultimate environment for people of all ages! We take great pride in being family-friendly with outstanding service to cater 
      to all your needs.  Come in and bowl on any of our 32 themed bowling lanes, or grab a bit to eat at our Award-winning Restaurant & lounge- The GutterBall! 
      We offer lane-side service for all your food and beverage needs which means you place the order, and it'll be delivered right to your lane. that ordering has never been easier. 
      There are so many special events and offers to choose from:  our late night Late Night Party, Cosmic X-Bowl, Professional Leagues, Public Bowling, 10 Pin Tap, and of course the Arcade.  
      Our promise to each and every guest is that you will have fun and leave with a smile.  Join us and be a part of what makes 12 Pins the Best Bowling Alley in Western Washington!</p>
</section><hr>

